Package: proteomicsdeqms
Title: Differential Expression Pipeline for TMT/LFQ Proteomics (limma + DEqMS)
Version: 1.0.0
Date: 2024-01-01
Authors@R: 
    person("Your", "Name", , "your.email@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    A complete, reproducible end-to-end pipeline for differential protein 
    expression analysis from PSM-level mass spectrometry data. Combines limma 
    with DEqMS PSM-count-aware variance correction for improved sensitivity 
    over standard approaches. Supports TMT and label-free quantification data.
    Outputs include: normalised matrices, volcano/MA/PCA plots, heatmaps, 
    CSV tables, and Markdown/PDF reports.
